INSTALL:

Dowsnload scripts and put it to:

Windows 7 or Vista:
c:\Users\User\AppData\Roaming\Adobe\Bridge CS4\Startup Scripts\
Windows XP:
c:\Documents and Settings\User\Application Data\Adobe\Bridge CS4\Startup Scripts\
restart Bridge

If you not see new Panel named as 'Stock palette', go to Preferenses -> Startup scripts -> enable checkbox ketwords-countes. Restart Bridge again.
